322
00:15:23,173 --> 00:15:27,177
♪ I thought I'd chase paradise
but I'll just settle for life. ♪

323
00:15:27,261 --> 00:15:28,387
♪ So tell me, tell me, ♪

324
00:15:28,470 --> 00:15:32,057
♪ Did I die when I was taught
how to lie. ♪

325
00:15:32,140 --> 00:15:32,766
